data.whatILove:
This Home features a level driveway that leads into a 2 Car garage.  The first floor is easy to access from the front entrance into the Foyer, Living room, dining room, gourmet Kitchen, Master bedroom and bath, guest bath and laundry room.  Wrap around deck features 3 decks. One is open with a view of the mountains.  One is screened in with a Dining  area/gas built in grill. One is enclosed with a Dining area/built in gas fireplace.  Views of the Mountains on the top and bottom deck. Outside stone stairs leading to downstairs. Inside stairs leads to 2nd floor downstairs which  is perfect for guests with 2 large Bedrooms, Bath, Sitting Area and Laundry Room and Kitchenette. Seperate Workroom and Storage Area.  500 gallon generator in case of a power outage. 2 Gas fireplaces... Gas Build in Grill and Cooktop. Granite in Kitchen and Baths. Heated Floors in Master and Guest Bath.
$10,000 Founder's Membership to Sky Valley Golf and Country Club.
